summary: This mod adds the stones of barenziah to the qasmoke cell for the lazy folk like me.
descriptionHtml:
If you are as lazy as me then you dont feel like shearching for all the stones of barenziah or maybe you just don like joining the college or the dark brotherhood just to complete this quest,if that's so this mod is for you,it adds all the 24 stones of barenziah to the qasmoke cell.
You can enter qasmoke by typing in the console(by pressing ~) coc qasmoke.

Enjoy!
author: vldi4
